    <h3>
        NEC Unified Communications Server</h3>
    <p>
        The UX5000 allows your organization to converge your voice and data network and
        benefit from the cost-saving advantages, convenience, and ease of use afforded by
        networked communication servers. By integrating diverse hardware components and
        software applications, NEC brings control of telephony features and related call
        information right to the user's PC, and provides advanced Computer Telephony Integration
        (CTI) throughout your organization.</p>
